{"type": "article", "id": 14959, "title": "一根线系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-16T07:29:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122443d06shyRNaM7i35PF.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这组椅子来自 SOHN，用一根金属管折出了后背和腿，并保持了平衡，有一种独特的艺术感。从不同侧面看过去，椅子都有一种奇特的视角，而当他们随意组合排列时，又有一种舞蹈的动态。SOHN 想要以此来打破传统，寻求新的突破，在他们为数不多的产品里，都能看到这种思想。<a href=\"http://www.sohn.work/one-liner-series-chair-1\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142332dPzprY6HwU3y4hbD.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142333pKbuYM1aIL4jixwS.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142334VS6vW3j21EgyGAQL.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142334Rz9pBd8tGjx6lUPZ.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}